{"tid":2294773,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉嫌於上周用滅火筒毀警員車輛　60歲男昨落網","createTime":"2020-11-21T09:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T10:02:03.000Z","uid":44209,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"01d1baf7959a98c27b51a4ce0af5446e30dc5e54","tid":2294773,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"上星期四(12日)下午3時許，葵涌發生針對警務人員的嚴重違法案件，有不法之徒懷疑在葵涌邨停車場，刻意用滅火筒破壞警務人員車輛並逃去，涉案私家車車窗損毀。葵青警區重案組、葵涌分區特遣隊以及雜項調查隊人員經深入調查後，昨日(20日)在青衣長亨邨拘捕一名60歲姓陳男子，涉嫌刑事毀壞。他現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkGvzih.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkGvzih.png&h=47b58964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c98c75471e21f0a7ae15ab0f93b3426e79ca0ccc","tid":2294773,"uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"60歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94b5d3ec14d082f7878e3af7ea882e68523939b","tid":2294773,"uid":50745,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:27:47.000Z","msg":"咁721啲白衣人落網未"},{"pid":"6975399df0b06e1bdfb0c069ae52c5b918faa024","tid":2294773,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"銀髮手足"},{"pid":"cad4eaec66085533c193d939f7256508362bc9ad","tid":2294773,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c05fc5e747e4475cb167c88b110a5b9a770dad","tid":2294773,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"係前輩"},{"pid":"af454ffc5425ac4e079279c30ce6971292f2c657","tid":2294773,"uid":36995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T09:31:50.000Z","msg":"係咪黑警勾人老婆<br />\n俾人報仇渣"},{"pid":"2a8b36793a93cafac2d2209dc73e5755b67e04ba","tid":2294773,"uid":54223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"